              "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n    \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"\"\r\n      alt\u003d\"App Icon\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eRetail Price Optimization Analytic App\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n      The Retail Optimal Pricing Analytical app lets you upload your retail data for easy pricing optimization.\r\n      It analyzes sales volume, retail and competitor pricing, and market share to train a model.\r\n      The app then forecasts prices and volumes and calculates SKU-specific Price Elasticity to guide optimal pricing decisions.\r\n      This helps maximize your market share and revenue efficiently.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eKey Features\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Effortlessly upload your Secondary Report Retail File to get started with pricing optimization.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e The app analyzes Weekly Sales Volume, Retail Pricing, Competitor Pricing, and Market Share to build a robust model.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e It trains on your data to suggest the most effective pricing model tailored to your business needs.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Provides precise forecasts for future sales volumes and optimal pricing points.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Calculates SKU-level Price Elasticity to support strategic pricing decisions.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eKey Insights\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Automatically derive new features from your data to enhance model accuracy.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Evaluate and choose the most effective pricing model for your data.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e View a ranked leaderboard of models based on performance metrics.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Forecast future sales impact based on price changes to support strategic planning.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n",
